<doc f='codebrowser/posix/glob.c' l='1258'>/* Like &apos;glob&apos;, but PATTERN is a final pathname component,
   and matches are searched for in DIRECTORY.
   The GLOB_NOSORT bit in FLAGS is ignored.  No sorting is ever done.
   The GLOB_APPEND flag is assumed to be set (always appends).  */</doc>
